"Let's talk business"-Giovanni

Giovanni Botventre, the most powerful man in Alhadid...well, he used to be anyway. Owner of an incredibly popular casino, Giovanni used his wealth to control the local authorities and get away with just about anything he wanted. We don't know much about his past, but much like most of Alhadid, we know he despised magic. What was his reason? Well, I'm not sure we'll ever know now that he's been "decommissioned".
